features: 🔎Easily Track Your AirTag - This magnetic AirTag holder (*AirTag not included) is compatible ONLY with Apple AirTag and won't interfere with the signal. Put your air tag inside this airtag case and attach the device to cars, trucks, motorbikes, bicycles, boats, trailers, containers, transformers, power tools, camping gear, construction and farm equipment, etc., can help track your valuable items.

🧲Powerful and Durable N52 Magnet - This magnetic airtag tracker holder features a powerful built-in N52 magnet for attachment to metal surfaces, and the air tag magnetic gps case won't fall off over bumps! So you don't have to worry about losing your tracking device and valuable items.

🛡️Sturdy Material & Full Protection - Crafted from high-quality PC material, this protective AirTag magnetic case offers exceptional strength and durability, better protecting your apple air tags from scratches, scuffs, drops, and damage in all-around.

💧Excellent Waterproof Performance - The waterproof AirTag holder is equipped with a high-quality silicone gasket to tightly seal the AirTag, ensuring its complete waterproof protection. No matter what the weather conditions are, your apple air tag device will stay dry and track your equipment perfectly.

👁️‍🗨️Discreet Design & 3M Strong Adhesive - The AirTag accessories offer an extra strong sticker for attaching to non-metal surfaces. This cement grey hidden airtag mount features a low-profile and mini design, ensuring that your apple airtags remain hidden from sight. You can track your valuables discreetly without attracting unnecessary attention.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Holds Airtag Snugly. Strong Magnet. Sleek Looking
reviews.reviewText: Holds Airtag Snugly. Strong Magnet. Looks nice with good build quality. Additionally I contacted support about a question, and they were top notch. 5 stars all around.Because the material is smooth-ish so if stuck to a very smooth surface it can slide around if there is movement. You can use the double sided 3M tape they provide but that somewhat defeats the purpose of wanting something magnetic and moveable. Solutions I used: (1) Used a rough sanding paper to scuff up the magnetic side a little - holds without a problem now. (2) Used a sticky tack circle to ensure it doesn't move at all, but not permanent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This AirTag from Klearlook does pass my waterproof test for now. The AirTag has a gasket that as long as it stays seated properly during assembly …should give good results. I mention this because the gasket is part of the exterior of the case.I chose this to attach a AirTag to farm equipment. If someone is buying this plans to take it backpacking cross country,…they would need to watch this gasket while sealing the AirTag initially as well. I plan to check the seal and the gasket 2 times per year….after a harsh winter with temperatures at negative 5-15F and after the harsh summer with temperatures above 105 F. Waterproof and durable mean different things to different people. This suits the need I had when ordering. I’m pleased with what I received.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: Great magnetic case for Apple air tag
reviews.reviewText: I have been testing the Apple air tag for a few days now and am very pleased. I was especially surprised how strong the magnet is! The air tag fits in easily. We put the case on my daughter’s bike when she went to school today and it stayed in place well - she then just pulled it off at school and attached it later when she rode home. The case itself is compact - slightly larger than a £2 coin. Overall I have been very impressed with the product and I would buy again/recommend to others.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: Minimalist and compact design for the AirTag
reviews.reviewText: I'd highly recommend this product for those wanting something discreet for their AirTag. The packaging was a sleek design, and the product looks and feels high quality (textured material, adding a premium feel to it)—additionally, minimal branding so it is discreet and does not draw unnecessary attention. The magnetic at the top will also help to keep your AirTag from rattling, but it fits like a glove. A product worth having if you want to keep your AirTag looking new and devoid of scratches.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This enclosure does little to add to the overall size of the AirTag while retaining a significant amount of durability. Once the case was tightened, I felt pretty confident that the tag was going to be secure.The O-ring inside the case does a great job and ensuring no water can penetrate the enclosure. The magnet took me by surprise with how well it stuck to exposed metal surfaces.So far I've been using it on PC trolleys, using solely the magnet and not the adhesive pads. Having placed it on my car for a trip to work, it was still attached. Highly impressed by the magnet.
